a-platforms.html&#34;,&#34;hrefvpm&#34;:&#34;/int/en/home/pipeline-and-products/platforms/mrna-platforms.html&#34;,&#34;hrefvps&#34;:&#34;/int/en/home/pipeline-and-products/platforms/mrna-platforms.html&#34;,&#34;role&#34;:null,&#34;rel&#34;:&#34;&#34;,&#34;active&#34;:false,&#34;asset&#34;:false,&#34;pdfinnerAsset&#34;:false,&#34;absolute&#34;:false},&#34;active&#34;:false,&#34;data&#34;:null,&#34;url&#34;:&#34;/int/en/home/pipeline-and-products/platforms/mrna-platforms.html&#34;,&#34;description&#34;:&#34;Discover BioNTech’s mRNA platforms, designed to revolutionize treatments in oncology and infectious diseases. Leveraging advanced mRNA technology, BioNTech develops personalized treatment approaches and vaccines that harness the potential of the immune system to fight disease.&#34;,&#34;children&#34;:[],&#34;level&#34;:2,&#34;title&#34;:&#34;mRNA platforms&#34;,&#34;overviewLinkTitle&#34;:&#34;mRNA platforms&#34;,&#34;enableOverviewInNavigation&#34;:false},{&#34;link&#34;:{&#34;target&#34;:null,&#34;text&#34;:&#34;Protein-based platforms&#34;,&#34;href&#34;:&#34;/int/en/home/pipeline-and-products/platforms/protein-based-platforms.html&#34;,&#34;hrefvpm&#34;:&#34;/int/en/home/pipeline-and-products/platforms/protein-based-platforms.html&#34;,&#34;hrefvps&#34;:&#34;/int/en/home/pipeline-and-products/platforms/protein-based-platforms.html&#34;,&#34;role&#34;:null,&#34;rel&#34;:&#34;&#34;,&#34;active&#34;:false,&#34;asset&#34;:false,&#34;pdfinnerAsset&#34;:false,&#34;absolute&#34;:false},&#34;active&#34;:false,&#34;data&#34;:null,&#34;url&#34;:&#34;/int/en/home/pipeline-and-products/platforms/protein-based-platforms.html&#34;,&#34;description&#34;:&#34;BioNTech’s protein-based platforms include antibodies, antibody-drug conjugates (ADCs) and synthetic lysins, designed to broaden therapeutic options in oncology and infectious diseases.&#34;,&#34;children&#34;:[],&#34;level&#34;:2,&#34;title&#34;:&#34;Protein-based platforms&#34;,&#34;overviewLinkTitle&#34;:&#34;Protein-based platforms&#34;,&#34;enableOverviewInNavigation&#34;:false},{&#34;link&#34;:{&#34;target&#34;:null,&#34;text&#34;:&#34;Cell therapy platforms&#34;,&#34;href&#34;:&#34;/int/en/home/pipeline-and-products/platforms/cell-therapy-platforms.html&#34;,&#34;hrefvpm&#34;:&#34;/int/en/home/pipeline-and-products/platforms/cell-therapy-platforms.html&#34;,&#34;hrefvps&#34;:&#34;/int/en/home/pipeline-and-products/platforms/cell-therapy-platforms.html&#34;,&#34;role&#34;:null,&#34;rel&#34;:&#34;&#34;,&#34;active&#34;:false,&#34;asset&#34;:false,&#34;pdfinnerAsset&#34;:false,&#34;absolute&#34;:false},&#34;active&#34;:false,&#34;data&#34;:null,&#34;url&#34;:&#34;/int/en/home/pipeline-and-products/platforms/cell-therapy-platforms.html&#34;,&#34;description&#34;:&#34;BioNTech’s cell therapy platforms leverage TCR approches and CAR-T approaches, enhanced by mRNA technology (CARVac), to develop next-generation engineered T cell therapies that target solid tumors and help advance the future of personalized immunotherapy.&#34;,&#34;children&#34;:[],&#34;level&#34;:2,&#34;title&#34;:&#34;Cell therapy platforms&#34;,&#34;overviewLinkTitle&#34;:&#34;Cell therapy platforms&#34;,&#34;enableOverviewInNavigation&#34;:false}],&#34;level&#34;:1,&#34;title&#34;:&#34;Platforms&#34;,&#34;overviewLinkTitle&#34;:&#34;Platforms&#34;,&#34;enableOverviewInNavigation&#34;:false},{&#34;link&#34;:{&#34;target&#34;:null,&#34;text&#34;:&#34;Clinical trials&#34;,&#34;href&#34;:&#34;/int/en/home/pipeline-and-products/clinical-trials.html&#34;,&#34;hrefvpm&#34;:&#34;/int/en/home/pipeline-and-products/clinical-trials.html&#34;,&#34;hrefvps&#34;:&#34;/int/en/home/pipeline-and-products/clinical-trials.html&#34;,&#34;role&#34;:null,&#34;rel&#34;:&#34;&#34;,&#34;active&#34;:false,&#34;asset&#34;:false,&#34;pdfinnerAsset&#34;:false,&#34;absolute&#34;:false},&#34;active&#34;:false,&#34;data&#34;:null,&#34;url&#34;:&#34;/int/en/home/pipeline-and-products/clinical-trials.html&#34;,&#34;description&#34;:&#34;BioNTec