</div>

    
    <div class="cmp-extended-text-media__content">
        
	
	<div class="cmp-text cmp-text--intro cmp-richtext">
		<h4>Infectious diseases</h4>
<p>We believe the technology behind our COVID-19 vaccine has potential against a range of other infectious diseases. Our COVID-19 vaccine efforts have demonstrated several advantages over the traditional vaccine development that we aim to translate into new mRNA vaccine programs targeting infectious diseases with a massive health burden.</p>

		
	</div>


        <div class="cmp-button-row cmp-button-row__align-">
	
	
		
			
