<div class="extended-text cmp-extended-text aem-GridColumn aem-GridColumn--default--12"><div id="extended-text-65da7e8194" class="cmp-extended-text__container ">
	
	
	<div class="cmp-text cmp-text--intro cmp-richtext">
		<p>We strive to exploit the full potential of the body’s immune system by combining powerful new therapeutic modalities and a diverse array of biological targets to successfully help address cancer, infectious diseases and other serious diseases.&nbsp;</p>

		
	</div>


	

	


